Every word uttered by my teacher

4
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:48,260
is an order to me!

5
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:08,030
I take the oath

6
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:12,130
that you will have
either Drupad at your feet

7
00:01:13,290 --> 00:01:16,000
or my severed head

8
00:01:16,190 --> 00:01:17,290
in your hands!

9
00:01:43,020 --> 00:01:44,020
Arjun

10
00:01:46,090 --> 00:01:49,070
your vow shall
indeed be fulfilled

11
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:51,100
but at my hands.

12
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,140
Father, His Highness

13
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,970
give the order
to launch an attack.

